px;\n  width: 60px;\n  opacity: 0.5;\n  z-index: 4;\n}\n</style>\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"top-block\">\n    <div class=\"step-tag\">\n      <div class=\"step-num-top\">02</div>\n      <div class=\"step-info\">\n        <span class=\"step-word-top\">Paso</span>\n        <span class=\"step-name-top\">Diagn&oacute;stico</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"headline-top\">No<br>adivi&shy;namos.</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"bottom-block\">\n    <div class=\"bg-glow\"></div>\n    <div class=\"quote-block\">\n      <div class=\"quote-text\">Cada falla tiene<br>una <span class=\"yellow\">causa real.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"quote-sub\">Corremos pruebas completas de hardware y software<br>antes de tocar una sola pieza.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"checks\">\n      <div class=\"check-card\">\n        <div class=\"check-icon\">&#128290;</div>\n        <div class=\"check-name\">Test de RAM</div>\n        <div class=\"check-desc\">Detectamos errores de memoria ocultos</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"check-card\">\n        <div class=\"check-icon\">&#128190;</div>\n        <div class=\"check-name\">Estado del disco</div>\n        <div class=\"check-desc\">SMART y sectores defectuosos</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"check-card\">\n        <div class=\"check-icon\">&#127777;</div>\n        <div class=\"check-name\">Temperaturas</div>\n        <div class=\"check-desc\">CPU, GPU y disipaci&oacute;n t&eacute;rmica</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"check-card\">\n        <div class=\"check-icon\">&#9889;</div>\n        <div class=\"check-name\">Fuente de poder</div>\n        <div class=\"check-desc\">Voltajes y estabilidad el&eacute;ctrica</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\" />\n</div>","previousVersions":[],"order":2,"notes":"Slide 3: Diagnóstico — Paso 02. Yellow top block / dark bottom with check cards."},{"id":"b1b603c9-3251-4568